---
title: Aubergine Saag			 with coriander rice and sliced chilli
description: Saag is an Indian dish which, along with added spices, can be made from spinach, finely chopped broccoli or an array of other greens. It's got a vibrant green colour that's striking on the plate and, thanks to the addition of coconut milk it's got a rich and creamy taste and texture too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R13_W17_IE_IEVCLC14146-3_Mainhigh-8a7115af.jpg
